text:
Amplify Agency has engaged Jackson White to provide services for the Premium fashion Series on behalf of Trend House. As consumers increasingly seek sustainable products, Australians are seeking better fashion solutions. As the campaign's brand advocate, Jackson White will deliver key communications across media and social channels. This campaign reinforces the brand's position in fashion.

INFLUENCER AGREEMENT

This agreement is between Trend House and the Influencer for Trend House Trends Campaign 2025.

COMMERCIAL TERMS:
- Total Fee: $7,745 AUD (inclusive of GST)
- Payment Terms: Net 30 days from invoice date
- Invoice Requirements: Tax invoice required upon completion

DELIVERABLES:
- 3 x Instagram posts

TERMS AND CONDITIONS:
- Engagement Period: 6 months
- Exclusivity Period: 12 weeks
- Territory: Australia
- Usage Rights: 18 months from campaign launch
- Content Rights: Trend House retains full commercial rights

COMPLIANCE:
- All content must comply with ACMA guidelines and ASA codes
- Content is subject to client approval before publication
- Disclosure requirements must be met per ACCC guidelines

LEGAL:
This agreement is governed by Australian law and subject to the jurisdiction of Australian courts.

Agreed terms are subject to final contract execution.
